Vibe Creating Prompt Skill
==========================

This project is an independent, community-made English/bilingual port of the
"Vibe Creating" (Vibe Filming) creative paradigm and its prompt-skill draft.

ORIGIN & ATTRIBUTION
--------------------
The Vibe Creating paradigm, the original "Vibe Creating 提示词 Skill.md" draft,
the four-layer prompt model, the decision framework, and the example prompts in
docs/examples/ all originate from:

    ByteDance / Volcengine (火山引擎)

and were published in their "Vibe Creating Practice Handbook," produced with the
Seedance 2.0 video-generation model.

This repository is NOT an official ByteDance / Volcengine product, is not
affiliated with or endorsed by them, and does not represent them. It exists to
make a publicly-shared methodology easier to adopt in English and across tools.

All trademarks — including "Seedance," "Volcengine," and "火山引擎" — are the
property of their respective owners.

CONTENT NOTES
-------------
- The example prompts have been translated to English with their tone and intent
  preserved; the original Chinese is included alongside for reference.
- The "literary visualization" examples are ORIGINAL PARAPHRASES written in the
  spirit of common narrative moods. They are not quotations of any real literary
  work, in keeping with the original handbook's stated intent to respect authors'
  rights. Do not treat them as authoritative quotations.

